OL,5,
OL,6,CG2003FShopping channel Price Drop TV
OL,7,Fbegins broadcasting.
OL,8,
OL,9,FIt was the first reverse auction
OL,10,Fchannel of its kind in the world. The
OL,11,Fchannel was owned by Bid Shopping.
OL,12,
OL,13,FOn 17th April 2014, the channel's owner
OL,14,FBid Shopping went into administration.
OL,15,FPrice Drop and its sister channel Shop
OL,16,Fat Bid were closed down with immediate
OL,17,Feffect.
